Short Description Use the magic of light to explore hidden worlds, solve challenging puzzles and defeat deadly beasts in award-winning Schein, possibly the trickiest platformer you’ll play all year.
The Project Schein is an award-winning, puzzle platformer that tells the story of a father who enters a mystical swamp in desperate search of his son.
